abstract: After a man stole an idling truck loaded with 2,000 pounds of the shellfish, employees at the company drove after him.
snippet: After a man stole an idling truck loaded with 2,000 pounds of the shellfish, employees at the company drove after him.
lead_paragraph: A poorly planned crustacean caper was foiled this week.

abstract: U.S. Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer on Thursday urged Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell to consider over the upcoming holiday recess allowing witnesses to testify at President Donald Trump's impeachment trial, Schumer spokesman Justin Goodman said.
snippet: U.S. Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer on Thursday urged Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell to consider over the upcoming holiday recess allowing witnesses to testify at President Donald Trump's impeachment trial, Schumer spokesman Justin...
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — U.S. Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer on Thursday urged Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell to consider over the upcoming holiday recess allowing witnesses to testify at President Donald Trump's impeachment trial, Schumer spokesman Justin Goodman said.
